# Novamedika2 - AI Assistant Configuration

## Project Overview
Full-stack medication search service with Telegram bot, OAC Class 3-in compliance (Belarus)

## Tech Stack
- **Backend:** FastAPI + Python, aiogram 3.x (Telegram), Celery + Redis
- **Frontend:** React 19 + Vite
- **Database:** PostgreSQL 17
- **Proxy:** Traefik v3.6
- **Monitoring:** Prometheus + Grafana + Loki + Promtail

## Critical Rules (.ai-rules.md)

### NEVER SAY:
- ❌ "✅ FULLY IMPLEMENTED"
- ❌ "Works perfectly"
- ❌ "Problem solved"
- ❌ "100% working"

### ALWAYS SAY:
- ✅ "Code changes applied according to specifications"
- ✅ "Ready for testing - requires your verification"
- ✅ "Changes made, awaiting confirmation"

### Required Response Structure:
```markdown
## Статус выполнения

**Что сделано:**
- [specific changes]

**Что НЕ проверено:**
- [what needs testing]

**Следующие шаги:**
1. [step 1]
2. [step 2]
```

## Quick Commands

### Diagnostics (agent/diagnostics.sh)
```bash
bash agent/diagnostics.sh all       # Full diagnostics
bash agent/diagnostics.sh status    # Container status
bash agent/diagnostics.sh logs      # Logs with error filtering
bash agent/diagnostics.sh backend   # Backend logs (last 500 lines)
bash agent/diagnostics.sh frontend  # Frontend + API tests
bash agent/diagnostics.sh bot       # Telegram bot diagnostics
bash agent/diagnostics.sh db        # Database + Redis stats
```

### Production Management
```bash
npm run prod:up              # Start all services
npm run prod:down            # Stop all services
npm run prod:restart         # Restart all
npm run prod:restart-backend # Restart backend only
npm run prod:logs            # View logs
npm run prod:ps              # Service status
```

### Security Checks
```bash
py oac/check_normative_docs.py    # OAC compliance
sh scripts/run-zap-scan.sh        # OWASP ZAP scan
```

